{"tid":1368514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[仲要幾多火頭]送中同黑警未完，政府已急不及待搞埋通識","createTime":"2019-07-26T13:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T13:55:58.000Z","uid":169859,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"69469e52c599cc84259f3a356900f4be701b5a2d","tid":1368514,"uid":169859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:31:57.000Z","msg":"教育局轉用文憑試作為本港高中課程的主要考試制度時，通識科為四個核心科目之一，而教育局轄下的「學校課程檢討專責小組」經研究後，建議維持通識作為核心必修科。但局長楊潤雄在昨日《星島日報》刊出的報道中，指社會上不少意見質疑通識科教材、甚至教師教學方法偏頗，透露政府不排除重新考慮通識科是否繼續必修。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/356821/%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E6%8C%87%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E9%80%9A%E8%AD%98%E5%BF%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%BF%85%E8%80%83-%E6%95%99%E5%8D%94-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E9%80%9A%E8%AD%98%E7%A7%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F356821%2F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25AD%2598%25E5%25BF%2585%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BF%2585%25E8%2580%2583-%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%258D%2594-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E9%25A0%2590%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25AD%2598%25E7%25A7%2591&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07gESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=424fb9e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/356821/%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E6%8C%87%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E9%80%9A%E8%AD%98%E5%BF%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%BF%85%E8%80%83-%E6%95%99%E5%8D%94-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E9%80%9A%E8%AD%98%E7%A7%91</a>"},{"pid":"14e40cf5da75e8538720c94bb7b137a3dd6eaf7b","tid":1368514,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"774